description: A LIGHT BRIGHT AND BEAUTIFUL 2BD CORNER CONDO AT THE BLAKE, with private outdoor space and garage parking. The home features walls of large windows and sliding doors to a lovely covered outdoor patio, large open plan concept with beautiful wood floors, upscale appliances, quartz counters, and in-home laundry. The primary bedroom comes with California Closets for added storage.The outdoor amenities include a private porch, common lounge area, and rooftop space with sweeping downtown views, complete with barbecue grill, dining, lounge areas, a pet area, and Corn-hole. The Blake also offers a beautiful gym, garage parking, and proximity to popular local spots like Lincoln, Capo, and Loco, the Farmers Market, as well as easy access to the Broadway T station, and walking distance to the beach. Plus, it’s pet-friendly! You will love the effortless urban living. It doesn't get better than this with unmatched amenities, convenience, in a secure building.
